Interface EnvironmentVariableServiceBindingLoader.ParsingStrategy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

    EnvironmentVariableServiceBindingLoader
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public static interface EnvironmentVariableServiceBindingLoader.ParsingStrategy
    Represents an algorithm to transform environment variables that can be obtained from the given environment variable reader into service bindings.
